
{
//EVENTS
//First Meeting
"FirstMeeting.0": "Where...?",
"FirstMeeting.1": "You!",
"FirstMeeting.2": "What is the meaning of this? Where are we?!",
"FirstMeeting.3": "Stardew Valley? Pelican Town?#$b#I have never heard of these places before!$8#$b# Are you trying to make a fool of this martial god?!$5",
"FirstMeeting.4": "You claim to not know me, General Ming Guang, Martial God of the North and God of Love?!$5#$b# .........................................................$2#$b# I suppose this truly isn't the Heavens or the Mortal Realm as I know it.$2",
"FirstMeeting.5": "Well, to be honest, the last thing I remember is descending from the Heavens to the Mortal Realm.$7#$b# I was to have a meeting with a beautiful lady, if you get what I mean.$3",
"FirstMeeting.6": "But instead of landing in the ice cold capital of the North, I ended up in this place.#$b# And somehow, this house here showed up at the same time.",
"FirstMeeting.7": "Strange...",
"FirstMeeting.8": "This requires further investigation. If you'll excuse me.$7",
"FirstMeeting.9": "What a strange person. Is he really a god? His clothes seemed out of place and the way he speaks was just as weird. Maybe I will find out the truth behind this. This valley is magical, after all.",
//Wizard talking to Farmer about Pei Ming
"WizardAboutPM.0": "Ah, @. It seems you have received my letter. Come on in.",
"WizardAboutPM.1": "It's about this new person that has emerged in the valley. I need to explain one or two things, since people are panicking.#$b#And you are attuned to magic, so you are the only one here who might be able to comprehend.#$b# Feel free to ask any questions you might have.",

"LoopingWizardQuestion.0": "Here is what I'd like to know...",
"LoopingWizardQuestion.1": "Can Pei Ming really be a God or is he just... y'know...?",
"LoopingWizardQuestion.2": "How did Pei Ming end up here then?",
"LoopingWizardQuestion.3": "I think I understand. Thanks.",

"WizAnswer1.0": "Ha! I see why you might think he is a little deluded.$2#$b# The people in Stardew Valley believe in Yoba, people in other places believe in other Gods. Are they real or not? We do not know. #$b# But their existence is not out of the realm of the possible. Maybe some Gods DO exist. #$b# I can detect an enormous amount of mana ever since Pei Ming showed up, so while I have nothing to confirm his alleged Godhood, I have even less to deny it.$2",

"WizAnswer2.0": "Very perceptive of you to ask.#$b# I have spoken to Pei Ming before. And my best guess is that somehow, he has become victim of a space-time distortion.#$b# He hails from a far away time from an even farther away place. It is no surprise that he is confused.#$b# Even more interesting is that his language is being automatically translated to ours... there are so many mysteries to this occurrence.#$b# The last time I met an accidental time traveller has been about a century ago, but I forgot what happened to them.",

"WizAnswer3.0": "Perfect. If there is anyone who is capable of befriending such a unique individual, I suppose it is you, @. Give it a try.",

//Haley's Question
"PMHaley.0": "Please wait!",
"PMHaley.1": "Yes? What is it, young lady?",
"PMHaley.2": "You are... a God of Love, right? That's what you tell everyone, at least. $4",
"PMHaley.3": "Ohoho!$9#$b# Indeed I am. Why do you ask?",
"PMHaley.4": "Well...",
"PMHaley.5": "I need your advice then!",
"PMHaley.6": "Yes...?",
"PMHaley.7": "What should I do to find my true love?!$2",
"PMHaley.8": "..........",
"PMHaley.9": "Ahem...",
"PMHaley.10": "Aha!",
"PMHaley.11": "There is one important rule!",
"PMHaley.12": "DON'T!",
"PMHaley.13": "FORCE!",
"PMHaley.14": "IT!",
"PMHaley.15": "Wow! I haven't thought about it like that yet!$8",
"PMHaley.16": "Hoho! See, love is not something that is forced. People will come to love you with time and care!",
"PMHaley.17": "You're so right, actually! You truly are a god of love!$8",
"PMHaley.18": "Thank you! I will stop looking for my true love then and let it happen when it's supposed to happen!",
"PMHaley.19": "Might ask Emily to ask the cards for me, though...",
"PMHaley.20": "Thanks for your words, God of Love! Talk to you soon! $1",
"PMHaley.21": "I didn't even say anything profund.",
"PMHaley.22": "I am the God of Love but I am not very well versed in  matters of the heart...#$b# But I will encourage everyone to pursue who they love, in a healthy manner, I suppose.",
"PMHaley.23": "I wonder if my blessings actually work in this place? But then again...",
"PMHaley.24": "People are only going to ask me about romantic partnerships, aren't they?",
"PMHaley.25": "sigh...",

//HEART EVENTS
//2 HEARTS
"PM2H.0": "Ah, @. I did not hear you coming. Do you need anything from this venerable one?",
"PM2H.1": "Me? Oh, I have been trying to make sense of all this mess.#$b# Landing here, having no way back yet...#$b# I refuse to acknowledge all these dwarf scrolls and elven books that offered me nothing but a waste of my time.$7",
"PM2H.2": "How difficult can it be?$2#$b# Are you trying to tell me that these ancient civilizations figured out enchanted weapons and computers,#$b# but none of them were curious enough to ask themselves about dimension-hopping?$7",
"PM2H.3": "Well, more like 'dimension-falling', I guess. My answers to why I showed up here remain the same as they were when we first met.",
"PM2H.4": "(What should I say?)",
"PM2H.5": "Have you tried speaking to the Wizard? Perhaps he would know.",
"PM2H.6": "Perhaps you got cursed.",
"PM2H.7": "The Wizard? $2#$b# A bumbling fool who stays cooped up in his tower and thinks I can't see him watching me? Please.$7",
"PM2H.8": "Cursed!?$8#$b# Who in their right mind would ever think to curse me, the General Ming Guang?$5#$b#.................#$b# Actually, nevermind.$9",
"PM2H.9": "Regardless, standing here and talking won't solve any problems. #$b# Since you're already here, lend me a hand, no?#$b# Perhaps by doubling our efforts, we could find something that would help with figuring out this mystery.$6",
"PM2H.10": "Two hours later...",
"PM2H.11": "...well, that was a fruitless search. I think we turned around every possible book in this library.$7#$b# How unfortunate.$7#$b# There's no point in looking for something that does not exist. Let's get out of there.$7",
"PM2H.12": "[Pei Ming looks frustrated, but then sighs.]",
"PM2H.13": "@, I..........#$b#...thank you for your help today.#$b#I appreciate it, even if I don't show it right now. It's just a lot to deal with, and having no results after so much time is agitating.#$b# But you took your time to look through these old books with me regardless.#$b# So, thank you. As a form of gratitude, allow me to invite you to a cup of tea one of these days!$6",
"PM2H.14": "Even if we didn't get closer to figuring out the reason why Pei Ming ended up in Pelican Town, I feel like our bond grew stronger!",

//3 HEARTS
"PM3H.0": "It's you.",
"PM3H.1": "Surprised to see me? Well... #$b# Admittedly, I was looking for something interesting to do. $7",
"PM3H.2": "I ventured deep into the mines to the lowest level but those critters were too easy to take care of.$7",
"PM3H.3": "What should I say?",
"PM3H.4": "Please take it easy.",
"PM3H.5": "I doubt anyone is a match for a deity such as you.",
"PM3H.6": "Take it easy? This is the first time in centuries I get any break at all.",
"PM3H.7": "Ah, so you DO believe my tale after all? $1#$b# That Harvey person claimed I was suffering from a 'traumatic brain injury' due to some impact. I don't get it. #$b# I landed on my feet?",
"PM3H.8": "It has been quite difficult, however. I am getting restless without the faintest idea of what to do about it. #$b# I used to fulfil people's prayers, slay evil ghosts, sleep ar- $3#$b#....................$6#$b# Sleep a lot.$9 ",
"PM3H.9": "And other than that, I spent time with my close companions or my descendant.",
"PM3H.10": "No, that descendant isn't my child.$8#$b# He's from my brother's side.$6#$b# Let's save the topic of children for another day, hahaha! $1",
"PM3H.11": "But I digress.",
"PM3H.12": "It seems as if Pei Ming is lonely here, even if he doesn't admit it directly.",
"PM3H.13": "(Suggest Pei Ming to...)",
"PM3H.14": "(...hang out at the Saloon together soon)",
"PM3H.15": "(...take a trip to the mountains together at a later point)",

"PM3HSaloon.0": "Oho, it's been a while since someone has been bold enough to invite me so. $3#$b# But I appreciate the idea. Thank you, I will send you a letter regarding the date and time as soon as I can.",

"PM3HMountains.0": "Oho, it's been a while since someone has been bold enough to invite me so. $3#$b# But I appreciate the idea. Thank you, I will send you a letter regarding the date and time as soon as I can.",

//4 HEARTS
"PM4H.0": "@! You actually came! $1",
"PM4H.1": "Despite the weather, you actually showed up. That is commendable, there is no one here because of it.#$b# Keep this up and you might actually ascend to Godhood yourself. $9",
"PM4H.2": "Actually, @, I have a request...#$b# Could we perhaps go somewhere else?",
"PM4H.3": "Follow me.",
"PM4H.4": "This is just the right spot for such a weather, don't you think?",
"PM4H.5": "Forgive me for spontaneously changing the location when you actually picked the other one for a reason. But is there anything better than sharing a bath with friends?",
"PM4H.6": "What do you think?",
"PM4H.7": "I agree, it's very relaxing!",
"PM4H.8": "Well, actually, I wish we could go back.",
"PM4H.9": "(nod silently)",
"PM4H.10": "Ha! The more I learn about you, the more I realize that we have a lot in common!$1",
"PM4H.11": "Why did you agree to come here in the first place then? #$b# Feel free to leave anytime!",
"PM4H.12": "What, cat got your tongue? $6#$b# Or is the sight of my body rendering you speechless? $3",
"PM4H.13": "Ohoho!",
"PM4H.14": "Well, regardless, I appreciate you joining me. This here is one of the few places that remind me of home, to be honest.",
"PM4H.15": "I used to go to the hot springs with my two best friends every now and then,#$b# which often was the only moment of respite we were granted.",
"PM4H.16": "(.......)",
"PM4H.17": "Sounds like your life as a god was very busy.",
"PM4H.18": "Sounds like those gatherings were fun, though!",
"PM4H.19": "Ha! That's true!$6#$b# But you know, @...#$b# Even if the chances to see my friends were few and all of us had a lot to do...#$b# I always enjoyed godhood.",
"PM4H.20": "We spent the rest of the time in the spa swimming and relaxing. It was fun! I should come here more often. Pei Ming, too, seems to have enjoyed himself.",


//5 HEARTS
"PM5H.0": "@! It's such a delight to see you. What brings you here?$1",
"PM5H.1": "You were in the area and decided to check on me? Why, you're going to make be blush, hoho! Aren't you a delight?$6#$b#Come on in, don't just stand by the door. I was going to leave, but how could I refuse your company? It has been a while since we caught up.#$b#Feel free to make yourself at home.$6",
"PM5H.2": "The letters are addressed to someone whose name you partially recognize.",
"PM5H.3": "Hm? Oh.#$b# Ohoho. Snooping around my personal work, are we now?$2#$b# Were you not taught anything about privacy? Or not sticking your nose where it does not belong?$2",
"PM5H.4": "Hoho, I jest, I jest! $1#$b# These are just... #$b# Ah. Well.",
"PM5H.5": "I have been trying to communicate with the ones in my realm, where I hail from.#$b# Since the communication array does not work in this place...#$b# I thought that maybe setting up a teleportation array and sending letters through it would do the job.",
"PM5H.6": "Ah, my bad. A communication array allows us to converse even if we are far apart. #$b# Think of it as some sort of... what did you call it? Telephone. Telephone in your mind.",
"PM5H.7": "I really hoped my plan would work.",
"PM5H.8": "It didn't. $7",
"PM5H.9": "...I suppose I'm simply... $7#$b# ...worried about a relative of mine. He's a good kid, just...$7#$b# a bit too emotional. Even if you wouldn't guess he was from just looking at him.$7#$b# And that causes him to make decisions that any sane person would regret. But not him.",
"PM5H.10": "He's my brother's descendant, but I took him under my wing once he ascended as Middle Court official.#$b# A Middle Court official is a godling that has been appointed by another god, an Upper Court official, who ascended because of their own achievements.#$b# But you don't really have to keep that in mind. Let's get back to the topic.#$b# My descendant, he...#$b# He was a hardworking little guy, taking his tasks seriously...#$b# but, well, a kid is still a kid, one that has lost everything and has witnessed the cruelties of strife.#$b#He made several bad choices, which led to his banishment. Because of that-$7",
"PM5H.11": "sigh",
"PM5H.12": "I just want to make sure that he keeps himself out of trouble again.#$b# But... none of these letters are going through the teleportation array, no matter how many times I try.$7",
"PM5H.13": "How annoying...",
"PM5H.14": "(What do I say?)",
"PM5H.15": "I'm sure he's worrying about you just as much.",
"PM5H.16": "Yeah, I get you. I miss my family, too. I haven't seen them in a while now.",
"PM5H.17": "Perhaps you should let go. You should accept that it won't work.",
"PM5H.18": "Heh. I hope he isn't. I don't need him to become a worrywart on top of being an emotional brat.",
"PM5H.19": "Have you? Well, I guess that's yet another thing we have in common.",

"PM5HGoodAnswer.0": "What a mess. You did not come over here to listen to me complain all the time, did you?$7#$b# Ah, please forgive this venerable one. The loneliness gets to me these days.",
"PM5HGoodAnswer.1": "But, I'm glad to have a kindred spirit to hear me out. Thank you, @. I will repay this debt one day.",
"PM5HGoodAnswer.2": "(...)",
"PM5HGoodAnswer.3": "There's no need for that. We're friends, after all!",
"PM5HGoodAnswer.4": "Yeah, you owe me one!",
"PM5HGoodAnswer.5": "Hoho, I suppose that's what we are!$1#$b# Now, why won't you join me for a warm beverage? I purchased a new blend of tea from that Caroline woman a few days ago.",
"PM5HGoodAnswer.6": "Tsk, such haste.$1#$b# Shall we start with a fresh cup of tea, perhaps?$6",

"PM5HBadAnswer.0": ".................$7#$b# perhaps you should leave.$2",
"PM5HBadAnswer.1": "sigh",
"PM5HBadAnswer.2": "Get out of my sight.$5",

