"Spring2": "Hoho! It is nice to see you, @. $2",
"Spring3": "Ever since I ended up here, I have been on the lookout for beautiful women.I am not sure if any of the ladies living here suit my refined tastes.#$e#$8 Hoh?! Men?! I mean...#$b# I would not say no to another man either, I suppose.#$b#$6. But I prefer women.",
"Spring4": "I heard the Adventurer's Guild mainly fights with swords.#$b# You want to know if I have expertise on sword fighting?#$b#$7 Let's change the topic.",

