"Birthday3": "You want to know how many birthdays I've had? $8#$b# At least 800, ha!$1",

"Summer1": "I don't really have a favorite season. Perhaps Winter? But during Summer, I can enjoy the beach and take a swim in the ocean. #$b# I am doing that in Winter as well, however.",
