"Summer3": " Hey, @, why don't we go for a swim together, just you and me? $3",

//Fall
"fall_28": "Ho! Can you feel it, @? Winter is coming. Exciting, isn't it? #$b# Have you prepared your farm already?$6#$e# Me? I have my coat dusted off and ready!$3",
"Fall1": "Greetings, @. I am curious about something. Fall is the perfect weather for warm beverages.#$b#$y 'Do you prefer tea, coffee or hot chocolate?_I like tea!_Hoho! You are the same as me then.$1_Coffee all the way._I am not averse to drinking coffee but there are so many different ways of drinking it regarding the amount of milk and sugar that the possibilities are overwhelming for this old General, ha._Hot chocolate!_Sweet.Just as sweet as you are.$9' ",
"Fall2": "I hate the smell of pickles. $7",
"Fall3": "Ever since I arrived here, I have learned about so many new things that do not exist where I'm from.#$b# For example - record players! Sam showed me something called 'vinyls' and if you place them in such a 'record player', you can listen to music!$8#$e#........you are saying that this is old technology?",
"Fall4": "Fall is the season for cozying up, I suppose. I am not one much for that, however.#$b#$y 'What about you?_I like cuddling!_Ah, is that so? Good for you._No, I am not too fond of it myself._I knew you'd understand me, @.$6'",
"Fall5": "I have been thinking about my descendant recently. I helped him ascend to Godhood and wanted him to inherit my position one day.#$b# A lot of things happened, though, and I was very disappointed of him. #$e# Yet sometimes, I can't help but wonder whether or not I might have been to strict.",

//Winter
"Winter1": " The snow in the Northern capital often piled up so high that it reached the roofs of the houses.#$b# Some mortals loved it. Some hated it.#$e# But hey, if they were so angry about it, they could've just moved to the South, no?$1",
"Winter2": "Truth be told, the weather in here is much milder than in my homeland. #$e# I guess living with a heater makes surviving easier for the villagers...#$b# Such an interesting device.$6 ",
"Winter3": "All this cold makes me crave some quality tanghulu again...$4#$b# Perhaps I should start using the kitchen in my residence more often.#$e# Hey, @, do you have some fruit in that fridge of yours that you wouldn't mind sharing? $3",
"Winter4": "I saw Vincent and Jas building something made of snow the other day.$#b# I don't know if it was supposed to represent any god of yours...#$b# but I certainly know someone who would pass out from anger if he saw something like that in his temple. Hah! $1",
"Winter5": "When I was a mortal still, my brothers and I used to build snow lions in our family's garden.#$b# The results varied.#$b# We weren't the most... artistically skilled bunch.$7#$e# Why do you think I became a soldier instead? $1",

