"AcceptGift(O)Cornucopia_Rose": "A rose, the ultimate symbol of elegance and beauty.#$b# I will find a proper vase for it. Thank you, @.#$b# Or wait...#$b# Did you give it to me because you fancy me? Hoho, you poor soul, this General will never be romantically available! $9",
"AcceptGift(O)FlashShifter.StardewValleyExpandedCP_Alligator": "AAAH?! WHAT IN THE WORLD?! IT'S TRYING TO EAT ME! $8",
"AcceptGift(O)FlashShifter.StardewValleyExpandedCP_Bonefish": "Hm. Would it surprise you if I told you that I knew of someone who kept things like these as pets? #$b# I hate them.$7",
"AcceptGift(O)FlashShifter.StardewValleyExpandedCP_Winter_Star_Rose": "Oh, what a gorgeous, gorgeous flower. I could glance at it all day. Beauty is such a fickle thing, don't you think,@?",
"AcceptGift(O)454": "Now that is an intersting fruit! You say its origins are in a distant past? Ha! #$b# That fruit is just like me! $9",
"AcceptGift(O)637": "Ah, now this is a fruit of divinity. Pomegranates, the gods among fruits.",
"AcceptGift(O)814": "Ink! I remember the scent of ink, the scent of scrolls and ink, to be precise. #$b# Reminds me of my studious friends. Thank you, @.",
"AcceptGift(O)852": "Impressive! Did you slay a dragon on your own?! $8",
"AcceptGift(O)void.NorthernHeartMelon_Tassel": "Is that...$8#$b# Did you make this yourself?! This is such fine craftmenship.$8#$b# I am truly impressed!#$b#",


"GiftTastePeiMing.love": "Hoho! Now that is certainly a treat.",
"GiftTastePeiMing.like": "Recognizing this General’s refined tastes? Wonderful.",
"GiftTastePeiMing.dislike": "Well, thank you, I suppose.",
"GiftTastePeiMing.hate": "How dare you-",
"GiftTastePeiMing.neutral": "I appreciate the gesture but I doubt I have use for this.",

"Peiming_EngagedRoommate": "So you want this God of Love to move in with you? A bold step.#$b# But I like your courage, so let me accept. $1",

//Conversation Topics
"cc_Complete": "I heard you restored the village's Community Center. That is an impressive feat, @.#$b# Where I am from, this would have been reason enough for you to ascend to Godhood!$1",
"cc_Bus": "I heard the object called 'bus' has been restored. What exactly is a bus? Do you ride it into war? It looks unsettling, to say the least.#$b# Like a very, very strange horse.$7",
"ElliottGone5": "Elliott has been gone for quite a while. I miss listening to him go and on on about his struggles as a storywriter.",
"gotPet": "Oh, so you have adopted a pet!$1#$b# $y 'What kind of pet did you get?_A cat! Meow!_Oh, a cat. I am personally more of a dog person, but you could say that I like cat...$6#$b#...boys! Hoho!$9_A dog, woof._How lovely. When I was a young boy, my father took me into the city...#$b#...and I adopted a dog there. The pup has been the most loyal being I have ever encountered but I had to leave her behind after I joined the army.'",
"married": "So you decided to walk the path of wedlock? Personally, that is something I do not wish for. I am a free spirit, after all. #$b# But as the God of Love, I do wish you all the best. You have my blessing, so to speak. $6",
"married_twice": "Oh, you married again? Is polygamy common here? No? Oh, you got divorced the first time around? I see.",
"divorced_twice": "Divorced again? Huh. #$b# Maybe third time's the charm then, hohoho! $9",
"gotPet_memory_oneyear": "A year ago, you adopted your first pet. How time flies.",
"cropMatured_417": "You harvested your first Sweet Gem Berry? Why don't you make tanghulu once you have several?",
"cropMatured_void.NorthernHeartMelon_NHMelon": "I can't believe it! You really managed to cultivate a Northern Heart Melon?$8#$b# I never thought it would be possible...",
"dating_Elliott": "You have commenced a romantic relationship with Elliott? While those are not the kind of relationships I personally understand, I wish for your love to prosper. #$e# I AM the God of Love, after all.$3",
"movieTheater": "I heard a movie theater has been built in the village. So what exactly is it? Is it like watching stage plays?",
"SterlingTrash": "This Sterling guy vomited into the trashcan. Disgusting and undisciplined.$7",
"SterlingDrugs": "Sterling has asked me for substances he could abuse. Hah, if only I had access to the Ghost City from here, I'd give him some and he would hopefully learn his lesson. $7",
"JunaSign": "I did read the writing on the sign. Juna certainly is... interesting.",
"JasperGone2": "I noticed that Jasper hasn't been around. Is he alright? I would hate for an entertaining man such as him to disappear.",
"JasperHomeA": "Finally, Jasper has returned. Perhaps I will go see him.",
"keahi_prank": "@, you reek. This reminds of when I ate a specific kind of candy once that was supposed to hide my presence from ghosts whose territory I infiltrated. $6#$b# I was then told that this candy makes me stink so badly that it even repels ghosts, can you believe that? And well, your smell repels ME. Good bye.",
"MeetTheCats": "Talking cats? That's unexpected but not the strangest thing I have witnessed. Ah, they are going to be annoying, no?",
"HaleysCakeWalk": "There were so many cakes...$8#$b# Haley did great.",
"joja_Complete": "You spent a big sum of your money for the Community Development Program, but I have to wonder... #$b# Why were you the only one donating at all?",
"Vinilla.Honeyfuggle_Arrival": "I can't particularly say I am fond of people hiding their identities behind a mask but this newcomer seems interesting. I wonder where they are from.",
"UnhelpfulAdvice": "I don't want to talk to you. $2 ",
"UnhelpfulAdvice2": "@, I mean it. I neither wish to see nor talk to you. Stop being clingy.$7",
"UnhelpfulAdvice3": "%Pei Ming heaves out an exasperated sigh. #$e# This can't go on like this.$5",

"AfterFirstMeeting_Abigail": "Have you heard those weird noises from the forest? There was a WOOOOSH and a BOOOOM!$1#$b# I checked and suddenly found a new house there! This is so exciting!$1",
"AfterFirstMeeting_Alex": "I heard a new house appeared in the forest all of a sudden. Do you think the person who lives in there is working out?",
"AfterFirstMeeting_Caroline": "Abigail is so excited about the sudden appearance of the new house. When we heard all those noises, she jumped up and down excitedly.$2#$b# I am worried about her.$2",
"AfterFirstMeeting_Clint": "Loud noise in the forest? No, I haven't heard anything. I was busy here.",
"AfterFirstMeeting_Demetrius": "You say a strange person showed up after the noises in the forest, claiming they are a God? I don't think this is anything science can explain.",
"AfterFirstMeeting_Elliott": "I moved to Pelican Town to have some piece and quiet while working on my novel, but there is always something new and extraordinary happening every single day. Like houses and gods showing up out of nowhere.#$b# Perhaps I should use these occurrences as inspiration!$1",
"AfterFirstMeeting_Emily": "Say that again, @?!$6#$b# An ancient deity descended from above, claiming to be a God of Love?!$6 If that is true, I really need to know more. This can only be an omen. Only time can tell whether or not it's a good one.",
"AfterFirstMeeting_Evelyn": "What eventful times we live in... may Yoba have mercy.",
"AfterFirstMeeting_George": "You say there was a man who claimed to be a god?#$b# Young people these days, they're good for nothing! Perhaps this guy should find a job!$3",
"AfterFirstMeeting_Gus": "No matter where this new person claiming to be a god is from, if they need food and drink, they will always be welcome in my saloon. #$b# This place is for everyone and we don't discriminate between gods and humans! Hahaha! $1",
"AfterFirstMeeting_Haley": "Ugh, Emily is all worked up over this 'god' or whatever.$3#$b#$y 'But if he actually is a god... do you think he looks good?_Yes, very!_Ha, then I might check him out!$1_No, he wasn't my type._Huh, really? Here I thought this was my chance.'",
"AfterFirstMeeting_Harvey": "A stranger claiming to be a god? #$b# Oh dear, perhaps you should send him to my clinic for a check-up.$8",
"AfterFirstMeeting_Jas": "I saw a man and a house fall from the sky! It was so scary...$2",
"AfterFirstMeeting_Krobus": "Hm, you think a deity accidentally showing up in the valley is strange?$1#$b# I wouldn't say so.$7",
"AfterFirstMeeting_Leah": "A lot of people here believe in Yoba. I don't really believe this newcomer is a god, but if he turns out to be, I would like to sculpt a statue of him.#$b# Just like people used to in old times!$1",
"AfterFirstMeeting_Leo": "A man fell from the sky? Did he have an accident?",
"AfterFirstMeeting_Lewis": "This newcomer in the Forest sounds like trouble. I will keep an eye on the situation.$2",
"AfterFirstMeeting_Linues": "You say a disoriented man appeared in the forest? Perhaps I will check on him later. I still have some fresh fruit in my tent.",
"AfterFirstMeeting_Marnie": "My poor cows got so startled from that noise! It took a while to calm them down. $3",
"AfterFirstMeeting_Maru": "I wonder what the recent developments in the forest mean for science and research. @, will you help me find out?$1",
"AfterFirstMeeting_Penny": "%Penny seems to be too shocked to talk to you.",
"AfterFirstMeeting_Pierre": "Great. Yet another occurrence Abigail can be weird about.$2",
"AfterFirstMeeting_Sam":"Finally, something interesting happening here. Do you reckon this sky guy likes to make music?",
"AfterFirstMeeting_Sebastian": "I am curious about this new fellow in the forest. Perhaps Abby, Sam and I will pay him a visit later.",
"AfterFirstMeeting_Shane": "Am I just REALLY drunk or did I really just see what I saw in the Forest?",
"AfterFirstMeeting_Olivia": "The 'God of Love'?#$b# Ohohoho!$1#$b# He either is very funny or very serious. #$b# If he truly is a god, I hope I am his type so we can share some fine wine together.$9",
"AfterFirstMeeting_Morgan": "I saw him! I saw the god! Magnus said that it's definitely in the realm of the possible.",
"AfterFirstMeeting_Claire": "Gods descending from the sky? Sure, why not. Can they also end retail jobs once and for all?",
"AfterFirstMeeting_Andy": "Yoba almighty, just what was that loud noise across my farm?",

////////roommate dialogue
//moving in accept
"PeimingRoommate0": "What an interesting choice to make. But remember that I can't cook at all. $1",
"PeimingRoommate1": "I hope we will enjoy each other's company. It has become quite lonely in my abode.",

"Spring_Peiming": "You know that I am a free spirit. We don't need to cling to each other day and night. #$b# So don't mind me if I wander around the valley.",
"Summer_Peiming": "Should I go to the beach? Or spend the day in the cool deep forest nearby?",
"Fall_Peiming": "Fall means it's time for chestnuts. Do chestnuts grow around the valley, I wonder?",
"Winter_Peiming": "It is quite chilly outside. Why don't you take a hot beverage for the road? [(O)614 (O)StardropTea (O)253 (O)Cornucopia_Eggnog (O)Cornucopia_HotChocolate (O)void.NorthernHeartMelon_LoveTea]#$e#",
"patio_Peiming": "Greetings, @. It sure is nice sitting by the fountain and trying to come up with some poetry.",
"Rainy_Day_0": "This weather calls for a warm drink! Here you go!$1 [(O)Cornucopia_HotChocolate (O)614 (O)253]",
"Rainy_Day_1": "No excuse to stay at home just because it's raining. I used to win battles in the worst of weather conditions. $3",
"Rainy_Day_2": "Sometimes, I do think of the Rain Master... #$b# Oh, she's an old... #$b# ...acquaintance of mine.",
"Rainy_Day_3": "What a weather, huh? While I don't personally mind the rain, I do dislike that it ruins my hair.",
"Rainy_Day_4": "I should read a book. I found some fun ones with black and white drawings. #$e# Have you ever read 'The Scum Villain's Self-Saving System'? #$b# I'm not sure whether or not I want to give it a read.",
"Rainy_Day_5": "It's been pouring for hours now, eh? I hope our crops won't go bad in a weather like this. It would be such a waste!",
"Indoor_Day": "@! Up bright and early, are you?$1#$b# Do you need some help on the farm today? Say the word, and consider it done by yours truly.$3#$e#",
"Indoor_Day_1": "Hey, @. Don't overextert yourself out there again, alright? I swear I can hear Harvey's gibberish in my sleep.",
"Indoor_Day_2": "I had a weird dream.#$b# There was this weird, white doll, and.......... $8#$e# You know what, forget it. Inviting evil spirits into this house is the last thing we should do.",
"Indoor_Day_3": "Perhaps we should go for a walk together today, hm?#$e# We could visit my old house, if you know what I mean.$3",
"Indoor_Day_4": "I opened the windows to let some fresh air in but I think a bee got inside. #$e# Don't worry, I will catch and release it when I spot it again, just like you taught me.",
"Indoor_Day_5": "I planned on making some pancakes but %pet somehow got its snout into the mix, so scrambled eggs it is.#$b# Bon appetit, @. [(O)194 (O)195 (O)201 (O)748 (O)766 (O)874]",
"Rainy_Night_0": "Rainy nights have something comforting about them, don't you think?",
"Rainy_Night_1": "Have you ever thought about how you and I are something like Sworn Brothers? $1",
"Rainy_Night_2": "I helped myself to a bit of wine today. Would you like me to pour you a glass while you tell me about your day, @?",
"Rainy_Night_3": "@! Welcome back. #$e# Would you like to join me for a quick game of weiqi before bed? I may even let you win.$3",
"Rainy_Night_4": "You look positively drenched, my friend.#$e# Get rid of these clothes and go sit in front of the fireplace, no?#$b# We can't have you catch a cold now! $8",
"Rainy_Night_5": "I stayed inside and meditated today. #$e# I think %pet sat on my lap at some point, too. Too bad you couldn't see it, @.",
"Indoor_Night_1": "Nights like these make me wonder who I could ask to have some fun with... #$e# Oh, stop looking at me like that! You know exactly that's what I like to do! $9",
"Indoor_Night_2": "Welcome back, @. It's good to see you around.",
"Indoor_Night_3": "...hm. #$b# %Pei Ming seems to be spaced out. #$b# Ah, @! Welcome back home. Forgive me, I have been thinking about my best friends.",
"Indoor_Night_4": "Good evening, @! Why don't we have a drink together? Here you go! $6 [(O)FlashShifter.StardewValleyExpandedCP_BlueMoonWine (O)873 (O)903 (O)Wildflour.AtelierGoods_Bonfire_Ale]",
"Indoor_Night_5": "Hoho!$9",
"funLeave_Peiming": "I will be heading out today to have some fun.$3#$e# A god has his hobbies and desires, too, after all. $9#$e# See you later!",
"funReturn_Peiming": "That was a nice outing. I hope your day has been pleasant as well.",
"Outdoor_Peiming": "Let me know if I can help you on the farm! These muscles aren't just for show. $3",
"Outdoor_0": "I think I will try to fish a bit today. Willy borrowed me one of his fishing rods and said something about 'having to find my inner peace'. How peaceful can you be when there's a whole carp struggling on the hook???",
"Outdoor_1": "Walking around the farm makes me appreciate little things in life. Have you heard how excited the cows are when you give them treats? #$b# I think I may just spoil them all day today!$1",
"Outdoor_2": "Hey, @. I couldn't sleep, so I've decided to go outside. #$e# I played with %pet a bit, too. Who would've thought they'd have so much energy in the morning.#$b# Reminds me of some of the gods from the Upper Court, hah!",
"Outdoor_3": "I think some birds think of me as a scarecrow. Just a few minutes ago, a sparrow sat on my head!",
"Outdoor_4": "I spoke with Sam, Abigail and Sebastian recently. #$b# They tried to make me use your modern slang - I must admit, I do not see the appeal.#$e# What the hell is a 'rizz'?",
"spouseRoom_Peiming": "So, what do you think of my little corner here? Fabulous, no?$1",
"Good_0": "I am grateful for having a friend such as you, even if our lives have been so very different.",
"Good_1": "Should you ever stumble into my time and space, just pray to one of my statues, okay? $3#$b# As soon as I hear from you, I'll appoint you as a deity! $9",
"Good_2": "%Pei Ming seems to be in a good mood and is humming a melody to himself. #$e# %Upon listening closely, you realize with shock... #$b# %...that it's 'Rick Astley - Never Gonna Give You Up'",
"Good_3": "Hey, <Player Name>. You should be proud of what you've achieved on this farm. Good job maintaining all that for so long!",
"Good_4": "The tassel you gave me? I keep it on me at all times. It reminds me of good things.",
"Good_5": "You...$#b# ...need to give me cooking lessons one of these days.$4",
"Good_6": "Should we start thinking about expanding this plot of land a bit? Hoho!",
"Good_7": "Would you like to watch my morning routine? I can show you some cool blade tricks, @!",
"Good_8": "I would love to introduce you to some of my friends one day, @.$1#$b# I'm sure you would enjoy their company, just as much as I'm enjoying yours.$6",
"Good_9": "$y If I ever were to return to my realm, would you like to come with me?_Temporarily, yes._Understandable. I would show you my palace and all kinds of sights then._No, I'd rather stay here._Too bad, but I can't blame you. Things are very different in my home realm.",
"Neutral_0": "Would you mind getting me some of your homemade wine one of these days? It's been a while and I'm craving some.",
"Neutral_1": "Hm… I'm craving some caviar today. And wine…",
"Neutral_2": "You shouldn't limit yourself to just me as your roommate, @. If there are other people you want to live with, go for it.",
"Neutral_3": "Hoho!$9",
"Neutral_4": "I have been somewhat bored as of late...",
"Neutral_5": "It's been one of these days where I direly miss my old friends. #$b# I never thought I'd ever feel this way.",
"Neutral_6": "@... #$b# What is 'internet'? #$e# Why are you refusing to explain it to me! $8",
"Neutral_7": "Sam has shown me a song called 'I know how to say', claiming it represents me quite well.#$e# I forgot the musician's name... Three-something?",
"Neutral_8": "Can we hang out again soon? I am getting lonely here, even if it embarasses me to admit that.",
"Neutral_9": "Want to spar with me? It's been a while since we did something togehter.",
"Bad_0": "I am under the impression that you are avoiding me.",
"Bad_1": "Is something the matter? We aren't talking as often as we used to.",
"Bad_2": "Listen, @. If you don't want me around anymore, just say the word and I'll pack up and leave.",
"Bad_3": "If only you knew how insufferable your obliviousness has been as of late.",
"Bad_4": "You don't have to cling to me, by all means.#$b# But would it hurt to talk to me every once in a while?",
"Bad_5": "Maybe I should move back into my house...",
"Bad_6": "......................$7",
"Bad_7": "%Pei Ming seems to be pouting.",
"Bad_8": "I suppose someone like you can only be jealous of my good looks and my great wit.",
"Bad_9": "I miss women. The ghostly ones, the mortal ones, the divine ones.#$b# I am bored out of my skin here and you are not even talking to me.",




