"PartnerDialogue4": "Good morning, @. I brewed some fresh tea before you woke up - here you go. [(O)614 (O)Wildflour.AtelierGoods_Alchemist_Blend_Tea (O)Wildflour.AtelierGoods_Blueberry_Matcha_Tea (O)Wildflour.AtelierGoods_Cherry_Blossom_Matcha_Tea (O)Wildflour.AtelierGoods_Cookie_Jar_Tea (O)Wildflour.AtelierGoods_Good_Thyme_Tea (O)Wildflour.AtelierGoods_Happy_Harvest_Tea (O)Wildflour.AtelierGoods_North_Pole_Tea (O)Wildflour.AtelierGoods_Pelican_Fog_Tea (O)Wildflour.AtelierGoods_Plum_Chai_Tea (O)Wildflour.AtelierGoods_Positivitea_Tea (O)Wildflour.AtelierGoods_Sun_Room_Tea (O)Wildflour.AtelierGoods_Sunny_Delight_Tea (O)Wildflour.AtelierGoods_Flavored_Tea (O)DN.SnS_ancientsweettea (O)Rafseazz.RSVCP_Matcha_Latte]#$b#Why won't we enjoy it together?$6 #$e#",
"PartnerDialogue5": "It is quite chilly outside. Why don't you take a hot beverage for the road? [(O)614 (O)StardropTea (O)253 (O)Cornucopia_Eggnog (O)Cornucopia_HotChocolate (O)void.NorthernHeartMelon_LoveTea]#$e#",

"Indoor_Day_0": "Try to not get into any trouble today, hm?#$b# We both know you have a talent for attracting that, hah!$6",

"Indoor_Night_0": "Gods don't need sleep - it's considered a waste of time. #$b# Still, I must admit that the late night tranquility does make my eyelids feel heavy...",

"funLeave1": "I will be out today - try to not pass out in the dirt again, hm?#$e# Oh, don't make that face, @! I wouldn't be teasing you about it if that had not happened four times by now!$1",
"funLeave2": "I think I will take a stroll through the valley today - should I find something interesting, I will make sure to bring it back. #$e# Hm? What do you mean? We have enough cryst- #$b# Preposterous! $8#$b# There's never enough of these beautiful gems to display on these shelves! #$e#",

