/////MAIL
"WizardLetter.title": "So about this General...",
"WizardLetter.text": "Hello, enlightened farmer @.^You have encountered the newcomer in the Forest. Let us talk about him.^Come to my abode as soon as you can.^ - Magnus R.",
"PMLibraryThanks.title": "You have my gratitude",
"PMLibraryThanks.text": "Greetings, @. ^I wanted to express my gratitude for your help the other day in the library. I was too upset to show properly, so please accept this token of appreciation for what you have done for me.^^ - General Ming Guang, Martial God of the North",
"PM4HSaloonLetter.title": "Your invitation.",
"PM4HSaloonLetter.text": "Dear @,^ As promised, I would like to take up on your offer of spending time together at the saloon. Let us meet there at 18:00. ^ - General Ming Guang, Martial God of the North",
"PM4HMountainsLetter.title": "Your invitation.",
"PM4HMountainsLetter.text": "Dear @,^ As promised, I would like to take up on your offer of hiking to the mountains. Let us meet there at 18:00. ^ - General Ming Guang, Martial God of the North",
"PMTanghuluLetter.title": "Tanghulu Recipe",
"PMTanghuluLetter.text": "Esteemed @,^^ I do not know anything about the preparation of foods but I do vaguely remember how Tanghulu was made. It's so easy that even I can make it myself, hoho! It's a sweet treat I remember fondly from the distant past. Let me know if you like it. ^^ - General Ming Guang, Martial God of the North",
"PMApologyLetter.title": "Let us start over. ",
"PMApologyLetter.text": "Greetings, @.^^ I have done some thinking since our last conversation. I don't think you are in the right, but moping about won't help my case either. In fact, it is quite immature to try to avoid you like this, so forgive my rare emotional response to your words. Let us try be better friends for each other; my doors will be open for you again. ^^ - General Ming Guang, Martial God of the North",
"SleepoverLetter.title": "Come over anytime!",
"SleepoverLetter.text": "Greetings @! ^^ I wanted to offer you the possibility to sleep at my place any time you need. So feel free to use my bed whenever you need it.  Additionally, I managed to set up a teleportation array from the Bus Stop to my house! ^^ - General Ming Guang, Martial God of The North",
"NHMSeedsLetter.title": "Northern Heart Melon seeds!",
"NHMSeedsLetter.text": "Esteemed @, ^^ the other day, I was taking a stroll to the desert as I heard that the dungeon there is a lot more challenging than the mines. However, a special trader caught my eye and I went to check out their wares. The good news: for some reason, they are selling Northern Heart Melon seeds! That is incredible, I thought they only existed in my time and location. Perhaps I shouldn't question where they got them from. I luckily had Prismatic Shards with me, so I am adding the seed package to this letter. Why don't you try growing a Northern Heart Melon plant? ^^ - General Ming Guang, Martial God of the North",
"GlazedHeartMelonLetter.title": "Cooking with the Northern Heart Melon.",
"GlazedHeartMelonLetter.text": "Greetings @! ^^ I would like to show you my gratitude for bringing me a fresh Northern Heart Melon. I am not a good cook but I added a recipe from my childhood made from this rare ingredient. Give it a try! ^^ - General Ming Guang, Martial God of the North",
"MovingInLetter.title": "Renovations for Pei Ming",
"MovingInLetter.text": "Dear @, ^^ Pei Ming approached me about adding more space to your farm so he can move in. Come see me in my workshop and we can talk about the details! ^^ Robin",

//////SCHEDULE STRINGS
"PeiMingHouse0": "Hoho, coming to see me at this time?$3",
"PeiMingHouse1": "Back in my day, I used to have a palace.#$e# So if I have to be honest, this shack here is a large downgrade.$2",
"PeiMingHouse2": "Some green tea to start such a gloomy morning is always a treat.",
"PeiMingHouse3": "Rain, huh? Luckily, it doesn't seem like this place will be affected by droughts anytime soon.",
"PeiMingHouse4": "Did you know that where I come from, there were Gods controlling the elements? #$b# Seeing that rain outside reminded me of someone.",
"PeiMingHouse5": "Being a Martial God won't be of much use here, I suppose. So I tried picking up a new hobby.",
"PeiMingHouse6": "Have you ever attempted writing poetry? Turns out this is hardly my field of expertise.",
"PeiMingHouse7": "To what do I owe the pleasure to see you here in this weather?$1#$e# Would you like some tea to warm up? I just brewed a whole pot.$6",
"PeiMingHouse8": "%Pei Ming looks relaxed.#$e# @! Fancy to see you in my abode again.$1#$b# Me? Oh, I simply enjoy the weather. It reminds me of my homeland.$6",
"PeiMingHouse9": "Well, the weather can't be THAT bad if you made an effort to visit me today, @! Hoho! $9",
"PeiMingHouse10": "Do you have too much time during winter, or are you just bored enough to come and see me so often?#$b# Not that I mind, heh.$3",
"PeiMingHouse11": "$y Do you grow anything on your farm this season?_Yes, I do._Hoho! Mortals' adaptability is truly fascinating to me.$1_No._That's a pity. I guess tending to animals is the way to go for you during the winter, hm?",

"PeiMingRainyOutdoor0": "I actually don't mind being outside in the rain.",
"PeiMingRainyOutdoor1": "Hello. Why don't you stay and enjoy the rain with me for a while? #$e# We can go back to my place afterwards.$3",
"PeiMingRainyOutdoor2": ".........(Pei Ming glances at you with a weird stare.)$2 #$b# HAHAHAHA! Farmer, you look so very funny all drenched from the rain. A sight to behold.$6",
"PeiMingRainyOutdoor3": "I wonder if I should pick up fishing?",

"PeiMingMines0": "I tend to get bored here so I went to check the mines.#$e# The monsters are still too weak here, so my boredom did not get resolved.$7",
"PeiMingMines1": "I flung a stone crab onto a slime and it just exploded.#$b# The slime, I mean.",
"PeiMingMines2": "I find these mines to be quite underwhelming. I miss having a challenge.",
"PeiMingMines3": "Even if I do not particularly enjoy myself in those mines, venturing there reminds me of the various times I accompanied my descendant during missions. #$e# I wonder how he is doing and where he is right now.$7",
"PeiMingMines4": "Have you heard the voice from over there? I want to know who's there! $1",

"PeiMingSummerBeach0": "Random: During such a Weather one simply must use the chance and take a dip in the sea.",
"PeiMingSummerBeach1": "Recently I learned of an ointment called 'sun screen'.#$e# Want to help me rub it on my back?$3",
"PeiMingSummerBeach2": "The waves of the ocean remind me of a very dear friend I haven't seen in a long time.#$b#...............hm.$7#$e# I think I will listen to the waves a little longer.$7",
"PeiMingSummerBeach3": "I love swimming. Those back muscles didn't build up on their own! $1",
"PeiMingSummerBeach4": "With all due respect, @... #$b# You are standing in the sun. Please move a step or two. $7",

"PeiMingBath0": "Lovely of you to join me today during this Green Rain, @.",
"PeiMingBath1": "There is nothing better to do in this weather than take a dip in the bath. I don't get why the villagers are so scared.",
"PeiMingBath2": "I used to be part of tight-knit friend trio.#$b# There were banquets in our realm every now and then and we would often go to the hot springs together afterwards.$1#$e# Hah...#$b# I miss them a lot. Don't tell anyone I said that. $4",
"PeiMingBath3": "%(Pei Ming seems to be zoned out. Best to leave him be before he starts flirting with you again.)",

"PeiMingBday0": "Ah, good morning, @. It is my birthday and I am a little melancholic about it. Please don't mind me.",
"PeiMingBday1": "The view over the valley from here is great but I can't help but miss the view from my old palace.#$e# On my birthday, I would often invite over my closest companions and enjoy freshly brewed tea, sitting at the balcony that overlooked the North together.",
"PeiMingBday2": "%It's Pei Ming's birthday but he seems to be lost in thought. Perhaps even someone like him needs a quiet moment to himself.",
"PeiMingBday3": "%Pei Ming is wistfully staring at the water.#$e# (mumbling)... it's been so long since I last saw him. A birthday without him feels shallow.$7 #$e# %Pei Ming doesn't notice your presence. You decide to leave him alone.",
"PeiMingBday4": "Hello, @. I was just reminiscing. #$b#$y 'Have you ever crossed the waters within a coffin?_I'm sorry, what?_Yeah, forget about it.$7_That's a little macabre._Life is macabre, little farmer.$7_Uhm... isn't it your birthday?_....ha. You remembered?$7#$b# Indeed it is. I am not in a festive mood, though.",
"PeiMingBday5": "This birthday in particular causes me to feel quite sad. But maybe you could help me, @?#$b#Why don't we go for a swim together? I just know you look great in swimwear.$3",
"PeiMingBday6": "All in all, if this birthday taught me anything, it's that I am glad to have you around, @. $6",

